<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="euc-kr">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NICE지키미</title>

    <script src="../../../js/zkm/rzm/jquery-1.11.3.js"></script>
    <script src="../../../js/zkm/rzm/jquery-ui.min.js"></script>
    <script src="../../../js/zkm/rzm/ui.common.js"></script>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../../css/zkm/rzm/common.css">
    <script type="text/javascript">
        mbHeader = { title: 'DSR 계산기', home: false, prev: true, menu: true };
    </script>
</head>

<body>
    <div id="wrap">
        <div id="skipNavi">
            <a href="#content">본문내용 바로가기</a>
        </div>
        <!-- header -->
        <script type="text/javascript" src="../../../bzw/inc/header.js"></script>
        <script type="text/javascript" src="../../../bzw/inc/breadcrumbs.js"></script>
        <!--// header -->

        <!-- container -->
        <div id="container">
            <div id="content">
                <div class="section">
                    
                    <div class="dsrResult">
                        <div class="finalDsrBox">
                            <strong>나신용님의 현재 DSR은</strong><br>
                            <strong class="pColor">1.85<span class="unit">%</span></strong>
                        </div>

                        <div class="resultTxt txtC">
                            <strong class="pColor">4<span class="unit">억</span> 6,140<span class="unit">만원</span></strong><br>
                            <strong>신용대출</strong>로 더 빌릴 수 있는 금액이에요.
                        </div>
                            
                        <dl class="resultDetail">
                            <div>
                                <dt><strong>은행</strong>에서</dt>
                                <dd class="bold">2<span class="unit">억</span> 6,000<span class="unit">만원</span></dd>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <dt><strong>저축은행 · 카드사</strong>에서</dt>
                                <dd class="bold pColor">4<span class="unit">억</span> 6,141<span class="unit">만원</span></dd>
                            </div>
                        </dl>

                        <div class="comp">
                            
                            <div class="txtC">
                                <span class="tag ga">DSR 40% 기준</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="resultTxt txtC">
                                <strong class="pColor">3<span class="unit">억</span> 6,000<span class="unit">만원</span></strong><br>
                                <strong>주택담보대출</strong>도 이만큼 빌릴 수 있어요.
                            </div>

                            <hr>

                            <div class="banLink">
                                <a href="#none" class="ico12">
                                <span>실제로는 더 많이 나올지도 몰라요.</span>
                                <strong>좀 더 정확하게 예측해보세요!</strong>
                                </a>
                            </div>

                            <div class="uiAcco infoTip">
                                <div class="uiAccoHeader">
                                    <button type="button" class="uiBtn">
                                        <span class="accoTitle">꼭 알아두세요!</span><span class="hidden">펼치기</span>
                                    </button>
                                </div>
                                <div class="uiAccoContent">
                                    <ul class="listDot">
                                        <li>DSR 계산기는 참고용으로만 사용해 주세요.</li>
                                        <li>DSR 계산기를 통해 제공하는 예상 대출 한도는 실제 대출 가능한 한도가 아닙니다.</li>
                                        <li>소득산정방식과 대출정보에 따라 결과는 달라질 수 있습니다.</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    

                    <div class="bottomActiveBtns">
						<div class="btns">
							<button type="button" class="btn primary"><span>다시 계산하기</span></button>
						</div>
					</div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!--// container -->
        <!-- footer -->
        <div class="footer"></div>
        <!--// footer -->
    </div>
</body>

</html>